### AudioToTranscript – VS 2022 HTTP Client Tests
### Open this file in VS 2022, click the green ▶ next to any request to run it.
### Requires: func start running in a terminal + Azurite running

@baseUrl = http://localhost:7071
@boundary = ----AudioTestBoundary

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Health check – does the host respond at all?
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health


# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# 2. POST /api/audio  (multipart: metadata + fake audio bytes)
#    Pipeline:EnableBlobStorage=true, others=false in local.settings.json
#    Expected: 202 Accepted  { "id": "...", "status": "queued" }
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
### Audio – D|FR (Fill Request)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audio
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary={{boundary}}

--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="metadata"
Content-Type: application/json

{"callType":"D|FR","caseId":"TEST-001","phone":"9794920458","timestamp":"1745000000000","brandId":"4600"}
--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="test.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

RIFF$   WAVEfmt
--{{boundary}}--


### Audio – FeedBack|DriverFeedback
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audio
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary={{boundary}}

--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="metadata"
Content-Type: application/json

{"callType":"FeedBack|DriverFeedback","caseId":"TEST-002","phone":"5551234567","timestamp":"1745000001000","brandId":"4600"}
--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="feedback.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

RIFF$   WAVEfmt
--{{boundary}}--


### Audio – unknown callType (should return 202 + log warning)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audio
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary={{boundary}}

--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="metadata"
Content-Type: application/json

{"callType":"UNKNOWN|CODE","caseId":"TEST-003","phone":"5559999999","timestamp":"1745000002000","brandId":"4600"}
--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="unknown.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

RIFF$   WAVEfmt
--{{boundary}}--


### Audio – missing required field (should return 400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/audio
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary={{boundary}}

--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="metadata"
Content-Type: application/json

{"callType":"D|FR","phone":"9794920458"}
--{{boundary}}
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audio"; filename="test.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

RIFF$   WAVEfmt
--{{boundary}}--


